hwCluster.description: HUAWEI-HGMP-MIB is defined and owned by Huawei. This MIB includes four parts: the cluster, stack, Neighbor Discovery Protocol (NDP), and Network Topology Discovery Protocol (NTDP). This MIB can monitor the cluster, stack and topology collection.
hwCluster.name: hwCluster

revisions.description: Modify the description of hgmpNTDPExplore and hgmpNTDPHopRange node.
Add hgmpNTDPExplore, hgmpNTDPTopoLinkTable and trap node hgmpNTDPTopoChange for NTDP function. Add hwNDPTrunkMemberEnable node for NDP function.
Fix the errors checked by a tool.
